CAVEATS

    I know there's a Task:: way of doing it, and I could also play around
    with [Prereqs] section of my dist.ini, and that using Dist::Zilla to
    make a Bundle:: is an overkill.

    But I simply like to stick with the idea that the first three modules
    (YAML, Term::ANSIColor, Object::ID) will be installed before the rest,
    disregarding the alphabetical order.

